- `strategies/{slug}/risk/SIZING-RULE.md`
- `strategies/{slug}/risk/LIMITS.md`
- `strategies/{slug}/risk/KILL-SWITCH.md`
- `strategies/{slug}/risk/RISK-DECISION-LOG.csv` — populated by the risk-overlay backtest.
- `backtests/{slug}/{YYYY-MM-DD-hhmm}-risk-overlay/REPORT.md`
